{"tid":390523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔡若蓮擎天半島豪宅單位02年買入","createTime":"2017-09-07T06:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T07:07:00.000Z","uid":47584,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd9cb047934461042619b688b036d98c6e020dd3","tid":390523,"uid":47584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:50:59.000Z","msg":"教育局副局長蔡若蓮兒子，今早11時許從豪宅擎天半島高處墮下，倒臥在9樓平台位置，急救後送院搶救，其後證實不治。據文件顯示，蔡若蓮申報的住宅為擎天半島41樓高層單位。<br />\n<br />\n該單位是蔡若蓮2002年以440萬購入，根據今日的估價，恆生銀行網上估價單位值1910萬，中銀估價為1929萬，渣打估價1942萬，相較買入價高近340%。"},{"pid":"142d6b620279730c23a32b4a7ff97304c470e93e","tid":390523,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:56:07.000Z","msg":"肥仔啦~"},{"pid":"e2a4b6e6fdf7d43c77a2ca41471b66a9e4f2a649","tid":390523,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:56:35.000Z","msg":"變兇宅最多打75折"},{"pid":"c6e2659e69c11da87a72685389f0b0447aeab0b9","tid":390523,"uid":71175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:58:00.000Z","msg":"440 宜家 400 尺都買唔到。。。。"},{"pid":"655acdc119e930b145672d40cbf33743ae46d116","tid":390523,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T07:05:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>440 宜家 400 尺都買唔到。。。。</blockquote><br />\n屯門舊樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1081cc737ff4d49ffcd9aa9160a04567737b5d","tid":390523,"uid":78574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T07:06:48.000Z","msg":"都係唔驚無人接貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6770826a05c5065fc9f7eda73e29b5017f7c1d2","tid":390523,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T07:07:00.000Z","msg":"當個仔用一千萬養<br />\n加埋兇宅75折<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打和啦super<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}